1) How many looping statement are there in java ?
Ans) 3 Looping statement in java 
     a) while statement
     b) for statement 
     c) do while statement


2) what is looping?
Ans) The repetition structure allows to perform then same sequence of statements repeatedly
until some condition is met.

3) What is exit controlled loop?
Ans) A loop with check the test condition before the execution of code is called exit controlled loop.


4)Write a program to print numbers from 1 to 10.
Ans) public class PrintNumbers
{
    public static void main(String[] args)
    {
        for(int i=1; i<=10; i++)
        {
            System.out.println(i);
        }
    }
}


5) what is while statement?
Ans) The while statement evaluates the body of the loop till the test condition is true .
